OL,3,CWater supplier to double compensation
OL,4,Cfor firms affected by Christmas outages
OL,6,FSouth East Water (SEW) has agreed to
OL,7,Fdouble compensation payments for Kent
OL,8,Fbusinesses affected during water
OL,9,Foutages last year.
OL,11,FThousands were left without water in
OL,12,Fthe Tunbridge Wells area - in November
OL,13,Fand December - due to an issue at the
OL,14,FPembury Treatment Works.
OL,16,FSEW has now agreed to set aside a
OL,17,F#1.2m compensation pot - up from
OL,18,F#600,000 - following pressure from
OL,19,Flocal politicians, including Tunbridge
OL,20,FWells MP Mike Martin.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
