OL,3,CWater supplier to double compensation
OL,4,Cfor firms affected by Christmas outages
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAffected businesses have until Friday,
OL,12,FJune 19 to make a claim with the
OL,13,Fcompany.
OL,15,FSEW has said it will pay out all
OL,16,Fsuccessful claims by the end of August.
