OL,3,CWater supplier to double compensation
OL,4,Cfor firms affected by Christmas outages
OL,6,FMartin said the firm's initial
OL,7,Fcompensation fund was "insulting to
OL,8,Fthe businesses who couldn't trade
OL,9,Fduring what is normally the busiest
OL,10,Ftime of the year".
OL,12,FHe called the development a
OL,13,F"significant victory for local
OL,14,Fbusinesses".
